# HANDOFF.md is an append-only handoff log edited on every branch and by both
# agents, so the same top section diverges constantly. Use git's built-in
# `union` merge driver: on a merge, keep BOTH sides' lines instead of emitting
# conflict markers. This means cross-branch merges never stop on HANDOFF.md.
# (Occasional duplicate lines may appear and can be tidied in a later edit.)
HANDOFF.md merge=union
